name: Image-registration-and-data-collection
tagline: An Image Registration tool in MATLAB using ImageJ and TurboReg
body:
# Image Registration and Data Collection

This is a collection of scripts to run ImageJ TurboReg on stacks of already finished .mat files from PCA analysis.

For more instructions, see the [wiki](https://github.com/mynamedoesntfi/Image-Registration-and-Data-Collection/wiki)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
